text: A phone case is a type of object that protects the phone from any collisions, like the floor or stone. It will also protect your phone from screen cracks, compoment damage, and to prevent your phone from any damage whatsoever. Some phone cases are just single-colored, some have designs, but some have literal art on them. And its not like all phone cases are the same, some are made out of silicone, plastic, rarely titanium or carbon steel. Category:Mobile phones
title: Phone case
